# ZARA Retail Sales Analysis – Power BI

## Project Overview
This project is based on a retail dataset inspired by ZARA clothing sales.
The goal was to analyse how product promotion and placement inside stores
influenced customer behaviour and sales performance.

## Business Objective
* Evaluate whether promotions increased product sales
* Understand customer purchasing behaviour
* Support business decision-making through data insights

## Tools Used
Power BI | Data Cleaning | Figma (Dashboard Design)

## Business Insights
* Promotions improved sales performance by approximately 47.62%
* Products placed in aisle positions achieved higher sales compared to end-cap and front-store placements
* Women’s category showed the highest purchase rate
* Promotional placement increased product price in certain positions while maintaining strong sales performance
* Total analysed profit reached 38.99M

